Developer Terms of Use
des:
Testimony FM is a Christian Radio station which is dedicated to serving the body of Christ. We are on the air everyday 24/7. Your edification is guaranteed. You will find uplifting songs, in-depth Bible teaching, social teaching and more. You may be lost in your thought or uncertain about tomorrow. We encourage you to spend one hour with us and you will not regret it. “Therefore, since we are surrounded by such a great cloud of witnesses, let us throw off everything that hinders and the sin that so easily entangles. And let us run with perseverance the race marked out for us, fixing our eyes on Jesus, the pioneer and perfecter of faith. For the joy set before him he endured the cross, scorning its shame, and sat down at the right hand of the throne of God.”
‭‭Hebrews‬ ‭12‬:‭1‬-‭3‬ ‭NIV‬‬
